" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Anterior shoulder dislocation on a scapular Y view",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 360px; height: 373px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The \"Y\" of this view is formed by the scapula's body, spine, and coracoid process. The glenoid normally falls in the center of the \"Y\" and is obscured by the humeral head. In this x-ray an anterior dislocation is present, and the humeral head appears&nbsp;anterior to the \"Y\".",
